---
---

<section id="process" class="section">
	<div class="container">
		<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
			<h2 class="section-title fade-in-up" style="margin-bottom: 0;">How It Works</h2>
			<span class="badge fade-in-up" style="margin-bottom: 0;">The Process</span>
			<p class="process-desc fade-in-up delay-100" style="margin-top: 0;">We take the guesswork out of your transformation. No random diets, no confused workouts—just a structured, proven path to your goals.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="timeline-container fade-in-up delay-200">
			<div class="timeline-line"></div>
			
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div class="timeline-dot">1</div>
				<div class="timeline-content glass-panel glass-panel-hover">
					<h3>In-Depth Assessment</h3>
					<p>We start by analyzing your current body metrics, medical history, lifestyle, and food preferences. Everything revolves around you and your schedule.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="timeline-item right">
				<div class="timeline-dot">2</div>
				<div class="timeline-content glass-panel glass-panel-hover">
					<h3>Custom Plan Generation</h3>
					<p>Within 4-5 days, I design your flexible diet tailored to your BMR—featuring foods you actually love—alongside home or gym workouts with full video guides.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div class="timeline-dot">3</div>
				<div class="timeline-content glass-panel glass-panel-hover">
					<h3>Weekly or Daily Tracking</h3>
					<p>We check in via WhatsApp (weekly or daily, depending on your package). We update your weight, review progress, and I adjust your plan to ensure you never plateau.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="timeline-item right">
				<div class="timeline-dot">4</div>
				<div class="timeline-content glass-panel glass-panel-hover">
					<h3>Crushing Your Goals</h3>
					<p>With zero cravings and consistent action, you achieve an incredible transformation and learn the sustainable habits required to keep it for life.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.badge {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 6px 16px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.1);
		color: var(--accent-color);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.3);
		border-radius: 30px;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.process-desc {
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 1rem auto 0 auto;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.timeline-container {
		position: relative;
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}

	.timeline-line {
		position: absolute;
		left: 50%;
		top: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-color), rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.1));
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		border-radius: 4px;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: flex-end;
		padding-right: 50%;
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.timeline-item.right {
		justify-content: flex-start;
		padding-right: 0;
		padding-left: 50%;
	}

	.timeline-dot {
		position: absolute;
		left: 50%;
		top: 20px;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		background: var(--bg-color);
		border: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
		border-radius: 50%;
		z-index: 2;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--accent-color);
		font-size: 1.2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.timeline-content {
		width: calc(100% - 50px);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		transition: transform var(--transition);
	}

	.timeline-item:not(.right) .timeline-content {
		margin-right: 50px;
	}

	.timeline-item.right .timeline-content {
		margin-left: 50px;
	}

	.timeline-content:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.timeline-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #fff;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.timeline-content p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.timeline-line {
			left: 20px;
		}

		.timeline-item {
			padding-right: 0;
			justify-content: flex-start;
		}

		.timeline-item.right {
			padding-left: 0;
		}

		.timeline-dot {
			left: 20px;
		}

		.timeline-item:not(.right) .timeline-content,
		.timeline-item.right .timeline-content {
			width: calc(100% - 60px);
			margin-left: 60px;
			margin-right: 0;
		}
	}
</style>
